overview:
Welcome to your portuguese gourmet products online shop

With our carefully chosen selection, you get the best and most awarded wines from the various portuguese regions, the exquisite canned goods from Conserveira de Lisboa, the olive oil and vinegar that are part of the portuguese tradition and of the Mediterranean Diet, as well as delicious compotes that will impress even the sharpest connoisseurs. And we haven’t forgotten the world renamed portuguese coffee, without which a meal cannot be completed. All in one place.
